                     <interp inst="t18180506-98-person857" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a constable. I was sent for; I found the tea in a basket, which hung in the cellar. The prisoner claimed the handkerchief it was wrapped in.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
